org.codice.ddf.registry.identification

Class RegistryIdPostIngestPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.registry.identification.RegistryIdPostIngestPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PostIngestPlugin

    public class RegistryIdPostIngestPlugin
extends Object
implements PostIngestPlugin
    The RegistryIdPostIngestPlugin collects a set of registry-ids that are currently in the system and makes them available to the IdentificationPlugin for duplication checking.

    Initially the catalog is queried to initialize the set of registry-ids. After that the list is maintained by the process methods for create and delete responses.
